title: I Still Haven't Gotten My Season Rewards???
body: Like the title suggests, I still haven't received my rewards for season 6. I finished as gold 5 and it has been 5 days since the rewards have started to be handed out.

replies.body: Ranked rewards are being distributed over the course over two weeks following the end of the ranked season; however, just to check a few points off the list, were you issued a chat restriction or suspension at any point during the previous season?
